title: Giants in the Earth: The Paleoburrows
itunes:title: Giants in the Earth: The Paleoburrows
description:
Enter the paleoburrows of South America, where evidence suggests construction not by human hands or tools but by giant claws – and for purposes we’re still trying to understand.
